name: The Sagacious Three
description:
"Little was known about The Sagacious Three except for the fact that they were worshipped in the villages that were situated along the banks of river Huskhuu. but recent findings at Ptalomon suggest that these three might have deeper impact to the religions that thrived within the third continent.."

-Hozien, Nama'en. "On The Origin of Deities".
